==Finnish==
===Etymology===
Derivative of ''[[musta]]''
===Noun===
'''mustalainen'''

#(''varying from neutral to pejorative'') [[gypsy]]

===Usage notes===
While many of the Finnish [[Roma]] community accept this term, it is official and better accepted to use the term [[romani]].

===Synonyms===
*[[mustilainen]] (dialect)
*[[romani]] (official)
*[[tumma]] (often used in plural case ''tummat'')

===Related terms===
*[[mustalaiskieli]]

